    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Although COVID-19 pediatric patients just account for 1% of the overall cases, they are nonnegligible invisible infection sources. We quantitatively analyzed the clinical and epidemiological features of 82 confirmed cases aged 0-16 admitted to Wuhan Children\u2019s Hospital, which are expected to shed some lights onto the pediatric diagnosis and therapy.</jats:p>",
